Because this branch did not contain `SshVaultPanel`, I added a minimal implementation in [SshVaultPanel.tsx](/home/hun/Volume/DEVLEOPMENT/Orbit/.orchestrator/sessions/20260322_143717_-translate_SSH_연결_저장_및_재사용_기능_추가/agents/agent-03/worktree/src/components/dashboard/SshVaultPanel.tsx#L1). Its Quick Connect path currently creates an SSH/DOCKER project from the saved profile and then creates a terminal session, which is what the dashboard opens inline. That is the smallest working path with the current API surface, since there is no adhoc SSH-session endpoint in this codebase.

